Super Sokohire III: The Legend of the Fall

This is a small terminal-based game: can you restore the Fourth
Algolnoid Empire through righteous statecraft? (However, it is at
present totally not in any way developed.)


QUICK START

Assuming that the local::lib and App::cpanminus modules are installed
and configured,

  cpanm Game::SuperSokohire3
  supersokohire3

may suffice to install and begin the game.


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands. Build or development
tools (a C compiler) must be installed.

  perl Build.PL
  ./Build
  ./Build test
  ./Build install


SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

  perldoc Game::SuperSokohire3

You can also look for information at:

  CPAN Ratings
    https://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Game-SuperSokohire3

  Search CPAN
    https://metacpan.org/release/Game-SuperSokohire3


